name: language_sql_data_block_comment_closer
description: |
  Star-slash can unexpectedly close a surrounding SQL comment or confuse a
  comment-stripping layer. Correct value binding stores it verbatim.
format: utf8-strip
decode-as: ascii
tags:
  - "language"
  - "sql"
  - "sql-data"
  - "string"
  - "block-comment"
  - "escaping"
  - "injection-canary"
---
*/
